data.description: Welcome to Cumberland Dr! Nested in the quiet and peaceful Highpoint neighborhood. This property is priced below market value, and get a lot of attention. A fantastic home that has been well maintained, this amazing 4 bed home features a pass through window in the kitchen leading to a spacious sunroom. What makes this home truly special is the sparkling in ground pool int he backyard! A five minute walk from 2 amazing parks with walking trails, playgrounds and water features. Easy access to shopping and dining. Make this your home today!
